description:
Phuahtu : Zakhuma Ralte & Hmuaka
Video : Chiangtea Videography
Audio : Recorded, mixed and performed by Hmuaka at A.W.R. studio, 7 day tlang Aizawl.

Lyrics
1.  Lei hringnun mawina leh ropuina,
  Kumhlun tur reng awm silo;
  Mitkhapkar mai a ni
  An lo awm a, an ral thuai \hin;
  Engmahlo mai an lo ni e.

  Aw Lalpa he hringnun lamtluang hi,
  Zawh dan tur ka thiam love;
  Kal dan min zirtir la,
  Nunkawng dik ka zawh zel theih nan,
  Nangmah chauh ka ngai em che,

   Nun hlimna ka zawn thin te,
   Ropuina ka zawn \hin te,
   Lalpa nang i tel siloh chuan;
   Nunhlimna leh lawmna
   Ropui san, hausakna te;
   An thlawkbo thuai \hin a,
   Khawiah nge an awm tak?
   Nang chu i awm reng si.

2.  Aw Lalpa i hmangaih ropuizia,
  Fak zawh rual a ni love;
  Ka sual min ngaidamtu
  I ropuizia puang dawn ila,
  Ka puang seng lo, a thuk e mai.
